44.2737, 143.8026, 143.9419, 144.0443, 144.1656, 144.2387, 144.492, 144.5648, 145.3153, 143.6861, 142.5297, 142.9578, 145.0989, 144.4743, 144.271, 145.0765, 144.9119, 145.5293, 150.2839, 154.5863, 154.9551, 154.8563, 153.7855, 155.9108, 157.0603, 159.0965, 159.5101, 157.6863, 156.1795, 156.7571, 155.602, 154.5501, 153.2936, 153.3065, 153.3337, 154.0556, 153.625, 152.7001, 152.2704, 153.1892, 153.4634, 154.8052, 156.222, 156.492, 157.2321, 157.3599, 157.3556, 156.2769, 157.5019, 156.4824, 157.2298, 156.1355, 158.372, 158.5287, 157.501, 158.1546, 160.575, 160.3411, 161.7057, 163.0304, 164.6616, 163.8814, 162.7236, 165.5806, 168.1308, 167.5895, 167.1687, 167.8686, 166.7892, 168.2966, 167.3227, 168.3508, 168.1021, 168.2133, 167.4649, 165.336, 166.4667, 166.6215, 166.8435, 164.3398, 162.3434, 163.9379, 165.1745, 164.3898, 161.5933, 160.4259, 159.5941, 158.7643, 161.0915, 161.2709, 157.7965, 156.7304, 157.0502, 153.4124, 155.9251, 155.229, 154.8514, 154.3209, 158.5449, 161.6229, 160.1757, 159.2967, 161.345, 159.6576, 159.182, 158.793, 156.4361, 157.9255, 157.6971, 154.985, 155.4807, 156.0608, 154.0756, 149.6334, 149.453, 148.2067, 147.9082, 145.7994, 142.1704, 145.0243, 145.2778, 144.2115, 146.0591, 143.1922, 143.4232, 140.3512, 140.8675, 142.3912, 143.1683, 142.3706, 144.3616, 141.3665, 140.0492, 142.2228, 141.2916, 144.1589, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>因子择时：截面离散度条件动量/反转</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报提出用宏观经济、金融市场和因子表现三个层次的择时变量预测选股因子收益。核心发现：市场波动率和收益离散度与反转/动量因子的有效性存在稳定的跨期相关性。高波动/高离散度环境下反转因子有效（前期下跌的品种未来反弹），低波动/低离散度环境下动量因子有效（前期强势品种继续走强）。</p>\n<p>翻译到商品期货：计算截面收益离散度的 Z-score 作为 regime 指标，与截面动量因子相乘得到时变信号。离散度高时信号翻转为反转逻辑，离散度低时保持动量逻辑。该因子捕捉了市场状态对动量/反转效应切换的预测能力。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.48</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>2.3%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.7%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-11.4%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.06</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3315</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.51</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.29</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.18 / 0.79</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.16</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.33</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.18</span></td><td>1.39</td><td>1.14</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.27</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.38</span></td><td>0.42</td><td>0.16</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.55</span></td><td>1.31</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.71</span></td><td>0.1</td><td>1.38</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.64</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 21 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 21 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>58</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3317</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>38.5</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>截面离散度:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\sigma_{cs,t} = \\text{std}(r_{i,t})_{i=1}^{N}, \\quad \\bar{\\sigma}_{cs,t}^{(w)} = \\frac{1}{w}\\sum_{s=t-w+1}^{t} \\sigma_{cs,s}</div>\n<p>离散度 regime Z-score:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">Z_{disp,t} = \\frac{\\bar{\\sigma}_{cs,t}^{(w)} - \\mu_{L}(\\bar{\\sigma}_{cs}^{(w)})}{\\sigma_{L}(\\bar{\\sigma}_{cs}^{(w)})}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\mu_L</span>, <span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_L</span> 是过去 <span class=\"math-tex\">L</span> 天的滚动均值和标准差。</p>\n<p>因子择时信号:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">S_{i,t} = -Z_{disp,t} \\times \\text{mom}_{i,t}^{(k)}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{mom}_{i,t}^{(k)} = P_{i,t}/P_{i,t-k} - 1</span> 是品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 的 <span class=\"math-tex\">k</span> 日动量。负号确保：高离散度（正 Z）翻转动量方向成为反转信号。</p>\n<p>仓位:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{pos}_{i,t} = \\text{rank}(S_{i,t}) \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{target}}{\\hat{\\sigma}_{i,t}}</div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1</strong> (Sharpe 0.55): 初始实现，尝试了波动率regime择时、离散度regime择时、波动率变化反转三类因子。离散度择时(21d momentum, 21d regime, 252d lookback)最优但换手率1.07过高。</p>\n<p><strong>R2</strong> (Sharpe 0.69): 扩展参数网格（momentum 5/10/21/63d, hold 5/10/21d），增加IC-gating。最优配置移到hold=10d，但turnover升至1.75。IC-gating无明显帮助。</p>\n<p><strong>R3</strong> (Sharpe 0.98): 关键突破——将momentum lookback延长至42d（更稳健的趋势信号），regime lookback缩短至126d（更快适应市场状态变化），增加regime信号的EMA平滑。最终最优: m42_r10_l126_h21，Sharpe从0.69跳升至0.98，turnover降至0.97。5个变体超过0.85。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货（57个活跃品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 月度换仓（21天）</li>\n<li><strong>信号类型</strong>: 截面因子（截面离散度条件的动量/反转切换）</li>\n<li><strong>冗余检查</strong>: 与因子库最大相关性 0.19，为新信号</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 2017年和2024年Sharpe为负，策略在市场regime持续单边时可能失效；研报原始逻辑依赖宏观/债市数据（PPI、利率、TED利差等），此处仅使用了可从商品数据计算的截面离散度作为regime指标，是原文的部分复现</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.25s</li>\n</ul>"}